item.title: Investors Still Favor Dollar as Economies Outside the US Look Weaker
item.description: Investors continue to favor the dollar over other major currencies due to the conviction that economic weakness is greater outside of the U.S. than inside it, UniCredit said.

item.title: Blue-Collar vs. White-Collar Pay: Why a Decadeslong Trend Is Flipping
